Hello,

Your  patience has truly been appreciated. A known issue was preventing eBay Store categories from being saved for clients that have an eBay Store when creating/editing eBay listing templates in the BigCommerce Control panel. We are pleased to announce that this issue has been resolved and eBay Store categories can now be saved when creating/editing eBay listing templates.

Please don't hesitate to contact us 24hrs a day if you have any other questions or concerns: https://support.bigcommerce.com/contact.php

